# FindFoundFast

- **Site:** findfoundfast.com — **photo guidance links** for deliveries/guests (no driver app), with both Permanent and Timed sharing options.
- **Flows:** (1) **Property manager** — one-time building setup, 4 photos, optional gate codes. (2) **Resident** — 5-char code login once, then choose **Permanent link** (no expiry) or **Timed link** (30m/1h/1d) as needed. (3) **Driver/guest** — tap link, see steps; timed links can show gate codes that auto-expire.
- **Marketing routes:** `/` minimal landing; `/how-it-works` tabs (**manager** default, then resident, driver).
- **Stack:** Next.js App Router, Tailwind (`fff` brand colors in `tailwind.config.js`), Supabase, Vercel. Fonts: DM Sans + Space Mono (`app/layout.js`).
- **Voice:** bold, fun, anti-frustration; taglines include “Google Maps for your food and your homies” / “FFFliping Cool”.

**Full product brief, tables, and editor notes:** repo root `AGENTS.md`.
